ZH: 我的侄女比我小三岁。
EN: My niece is three years younger than me.

ZH: 她是我最喜欢的侄女。
EN: She is my favorite niece.

ZH: 我的侄女今年已经上小学了。
EN: My niece has already started primary school this year.

ZH: 侄女非常聪明，总是取得好成绩。
EN: My niece is very smart and always gets good grades.

ZH: 我每个周末都会带侄女去公园玩。
EN: I take my niece to the park every weekend.

ZH: 侄女喜欢读书，她有一个很大的书架。
EN: My niece loves to read, she has a large bookshelf.

ZH: 我给侄女买了一本新的儿童百科。
EN: I bought my niece a new children's encyclopedia.

ZH: 侄女喜欢唱歌和跳舞。
EN: My niece enjoys singing and dancing.

ZH: 侄女今天生日，我要给她买一份特别的礼物。
EN: It's my niece's birthday today, I want to buy her a special gift.

ZH: 侄女长得越来越漂亮了。
EN: My niece is getting more and more beautiful.

ZH: 我每年都会给侄女寄生日卡片。
EN: I send birthday cards to my niece every year.

ZH: 侄女非常喜欢小动物，她养了一只小猫。
EN: My niece loves animals, and she has a pet cat.

ZH: 我的侄女有一个漂亮的小花园，她经常去种花。
EN: My niece has a beautiful small garden, and she enjoys planting flowers.

ZH: 侄女会弹钢琴和吉他。
EN: My niece can play the piano and the guitar.

ZH: 侄女爱吃冰淇淋。
EN: My niece loves eating ice cream.

ZH: 我的侄女很懂事，总是乖乖听话。
EN: My niece is very sensible and always obedient.

ZH: 侄女梦想成为一名医生。
EN: My niece dreams of becoming a doctor.

ZH: 我和侄女一起看了一部新电影。
EN: I watched a new movie with my niece.

ZH: 每年放假时，侄女都会回来探望我们。
EN: My niece comes to visit us every year during holidays.

ZH: 侄女经常给我写信，我们保持着良好的联系。
EN: My niece often writes letters to me, and we have maintained good contact.
